brecksblog README

A high performance blog in 50 lines of code(and 1 .htaccess file). No MySQL needed!
Stores entries as text files. Doesn't do any type of voting or comments,
Includes widgets for submitting to social networks, email lists, etc.
If you want stats, add Google analytics. If you want comments, add Disqus,
If you want voting, submit to social networking sites.
You want great html, go somewhere else